00:59:02.751 --> 00:59:05.629
DIRECTOR SONG SEOKYUNG

00:59:06.296 --> 00:59:07.339
CHA JINWOO

00:59:08.590 --> 00:59:13.053
NO ESTOY EN CASA Y ES TARDE,
